            <lg xml:id="TK411">
<l>celvattuṭ celvañ ceviccelva maccelvañ</l>
<l>celvattu ḷellān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wealth (gained) by the ear is wealth of wealth that wealth is the chief of all wealth.</l>
            </lg>
